title: Charch in for PA #92Noon! 9a Hour 5/13 - Gorg/Turbo Traxxx w/ Cory Cove, Sauce & Hawk
description: Charch fills in for PA and delivers a passionate monologue about the sad and pathetic end to the Wild season, Kevin Gorg calls in to share his thoughts, and Charch debuts a new game called Turbo Traxxx with Cory Cove, Paul "Meatsauce" Lamber and Chris Hawkey as contestants!
